      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the appropriate Federal banking agencies to establish a 3-year phase-in period for de novo financial institutions to comply with Federal capital standards, to provide relief for de novo rural community banks, and for other purposes.</title>
